(() => {

const starFull = '<img width="14px" alt="star-full" src="data:image/png;base64,">';
const starEmpty = '<img width="14px" style="filter: invert(80%);" src="https://image.flaticon.com/icons/png/512/130/130188.png" alt="star-empty">'

};
